  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="246"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="eng" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle centre">
            <p>Registered No. 1268 of <date calendar="#gregorian">1886</date></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#farajbSaid">فرج سعيد باجوره</persName>
               ان عليه 
               <persName ref="#jairam">لزيرام بن سيوه البانياني</persName>
               وكيل السركار ثمانية و عشرون قرشاً صرف
               <lb/>البلد و قد باع له بحقه هذا اللذي في ارض 
               <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">باجمويو</placeName>
               مجاور بيت 
               <persName ref="#nasserbHamad">ناصر بن حمد</persName>
               و بيت 
               <persName ref="#habashAlZadjali">حبش الزدجالي</persName> 
               <lb/>بيعاً قطعاً تاريخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">يوم
               <num>٦</num> 
               في شهر شعبان سنة
               <num>١٢٩٢</num></date>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#farajbSaid">Faraj [bin] Said Bajura</persName>
                acknowledges that he owes
               <persName ref="#jairam">Jairam bin Shivji Al-Banyani</persName>, the agent of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref>,
               <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="28">twenty-eight <ref type="glossary"
                     target="#gl_qirsh">qirsh</ref></measure>, in the currency of
               <lb/>the town, and that he has sold him his right in the land in
               <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">Bagamoyo</placeName>
                that neighbors the house of
               <persName ref="#nasserbHamad">Nasser bin Hamad</persName>
                and the house of
               <persName ref="#habashAlZadjali">Habash Al-Zadjali</persName>
               <lb/>[and this is] a complete sale on
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">6 Shaʿban 1292</date>.<note>This date is equivalent to 7 September 1875 CE.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="ara" type="witness">
            <p><lb/>و شهد بذلك
               <persName ref="#ubaidbAwadh">عبيد بن عوض بن غانم</persName>
                كتبه الحقير الى ربه
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#abdullahbAli">عبدالله بن علي بن سالم بن عبدالسلام</persName> بيده
            <lb/>
              و شهد بذلك
               <persName ref="#ahmadbMubarak">احمد بن مبارك الراعي</persName>
               <lb/> و كتبه بيده
                و شهد بذلك
               <persName ref="#fairuz">فيروز</persName>
                تابع
               <persName ref="#sayyidBarghash">السيد برغش</persName>
                و كتبه بيده </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p><lb/>And this was witnessed by
               <persName ref="#ubaidbAwadh">Ubaid bin Awadh bin Ghanim</persName>, written by the wretched for his Lord,
               <lb/><persName ref="#abdullahbAli">Abdullah bin Ali bin Salem bin Abdussalam</persName>, in his own hand.
               <lb/>And this was witnessed by
               <persName ref="#ahmadbMubarak">Ahmad bin Mubarak
                <lb/>Al-Rai</persName>
               and written by his own hand.
               <lb/>And this was witnessed by <persName ref="#fairuz">Fairuz</persName>,
               <lb/>the slave of <persName ref="#sayyidBarghash">Sayyid Barghash [Al-Busaidi, Sultan of Zanzibar]</persName> and written by his own hand.<note>These are scribal copies of the witness statements that were written on the original document.</note> 
            </p>
            </div>
         
        
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="eng" type="clericalNotes" rend="bottom centre">
            <p>
               <lb/>Dated <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">6th Shaban 1292</date><note>This date is written in the same line as the last line of the Arabic maintext above.</note>
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <lb/>Deed of Sale of a house at <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">Bagamoyo</placeName>
               <lb/>Sold by <persName ref="#farajbSaid">Faraj Saeed Bajur</persName> for <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="28">$28</measure>
               <lb/>To <persName ref="#jairam">Jairam Sevji</persName> The Agent of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">Serkar [Sarkar]</ref>
               <lb/>produced by <persName ref="#krishnadas">Kersendas [Krishnadas]</persName>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="eng" type="authorisation" rend="bottom centre">
            <p>
               <placeName ref="#zanzibar">Zanzibar</placeName> <date calendar="#gregorian">29th December 1886</date> <persName ref="#ernestBerkeley">Ernest Berkeley</persName><note>This name is signed.</note> <choice><abbr>H. M.</abbr><expan>Her Majesty's</expan></choice> Vice Consul <placeName ref="#zanzibar">Zanzibar</placeName> <figure><figDesc>A small rectangle, containing the numbers 5/~. Below the box the words 'on Deed' are written.</figDesc></figure>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
